View Usage Statistics for Einstein Discovery

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS
To view Einstein Discovery usage statistics:	Manage Einstein Discovery

From Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Discovery.
Under Einstein Discovery and Einstein Discovery in Reports, select Usage.

Times and dates are based on your orgâ€™s default time zone.

STATISTIC	DESCRIPTION
Number of predictions run today	Total number of predictions using Automated Prediction Writeback.
Number of model versions created today	Total number of all models created since 12:00 AM.
Number of model versions currently being created	Total number of model versions being created in your org.
Number of prediction API calls run today	Total number of on-demand predictions, including requests from Einstein Prediction Service, Apex, Flow Builder, and Lightning Components.
Number of model versions created this month	Total number of all models created since 12:00 AM on the first day of the current month.
